data.name: ForbiddenCharacters
desc: Locale (mostly CJK) dependent characters that are forbidden at the start or end of a line.
Returned by XLocaleData::getForbiddenCharacters() and used with XForbiddenCharacters methods.

items.name: beginLine
lines: Characters forbidden at the start of a line.

items.name: endLine
lines: Characters forbidden at the end of a line.
